properties.areaDesc: Sand Island to Bayfield WI; Port Wing to Sand Island WI
properties.headline: Gale Warning issued January 4 at 3:32PM CST until January 6 at 12:00AM CST by NWS Duluth MN
properties.description:
* WHAT...West winds 20 to 30 knots with gusts up to 35 knots and
waves 4 to 7 feet expected. Waves occasionally to 9 feet.

* WHERE...Port Wing to Sand Island WI and Sand Island to
Bayfield WI.

* WHEN...From noon Sunday to midnight CST Sunday night.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds will cause hazardous waves which could
capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should alter plans to avoid these hazardous conditions.
Remain in port, seek safe harbor, alter course, and/or secure the
vessel for severe conditions.

NWSheadline: GALE WARNING IN EFFECT FROM NOON SUNDAY TO MIDNIGHT CST SUNDAY NIGHT
